data.text: Mishti is an Indian film actress. She made her Bollywood debut with Subhash Ghai's film Kaanchi: The Unbreakable, her Tollywood debut with the Nithiin-A. Karunakaran film Chinnadana Nee Kosam. and her Mollywood debut with Prithviraj Sukumaran and Jinu Abraham's film Adam JoanMishti's next Telugu film, Columbus, stars Sumanth Ashwin and is produced by MS Raju. She returned to Bollywood with Indra Kumar's Great Grand Masti, the third film in the Masti.
